OL,5, The use of pre-recorded evidence from  
OL,6, victims and witnesses of crimes such as
OL,7, rape has been rolled out across all    
OL,8, crown courts in England and Wales.     
OL,10,FThe technology will be available from  
OL,11,FMonday at a final 20 courts including  
OL,12,Fthose in London, the South East and    
OL,13,FEast of England, the Ministry of       
OL,14,FJustice said.                          
OL,16,FIt marks the end of a national rollout.
OL,18,FJustice Secretary, Brandon Lewis, said 
OL,19,Fit spared victims "testifying under the
OL,20,Ffull glare of a courtroom".            
